{"type":"answer","id":156313,"parentType":"question","parentId":17731,"uid":20551,"contents":"每年都会爆发季节性流感，每次流感爆发可以感染数亿人，致死几十万人，但大多数人不会把常见的流感当作一回事。H1N1的传染性和致死率甚至低于常见的季节性流感，和肺炎根本没有可比性。用H1N1去指责发达国家的卫生系统，就像埃博拉疫区指责美国感冒患者多一样可笑。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/SEKlCt7.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SEKlCt7.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/SEKlCt7.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n此外流感本身不会致死，继发症状比如心血管意外或者<b>肺炎</b>才会致死。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2009_flu_untrusted fake 2049bbs（钓鱼网站）/wiki/2009_flu_pandemic#Comparisons_to_other_pandemics_and_epidemics</a>\t\t</div>\n\t\t<!-- end 回答 -->\n\t</div>\n\t<div class=\" mod-footer\"=\"\">\n\n</a><div class=\"meta clearfix\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2009_flu_untrusted fake 2049bbs（钓鱼网站）/wiki/2009_flu_pandemic#Comparisons_to_other_pandemics_and_epidemics</a>\t\t</div>\n\t\t<!-- end 回答 -->\n\t</div>\n\t<div class=\" mod-footer\"=\"\">\n<span class=\"aw-small-text pull-right\">2020-02-09</span>\n\n<span class=\"operate aw-vote-ui\">\n</span></a><a href=\"javascript:;\" class=\"agree disabled\">\n<i class=\"icon icon-agree\"></i> <b class=\"count\">7</b>\n</a>\n\n\n<span class=\"operate\">\n<a href=\"javascript:;\" onclick=\"toggle_disscusion($(this));\" class=\"aw-add-comment\" data-id=\"156313\" data-type=\"answer\" data-comment-count=\"0\"><i class=\"icon icon-comment\"></i> 0</a>\n</span>\n\n<div class=\"more-operate\">\n<a href=\"/vote/log/item_type-answer__item_id-156313\" class=\"aw-small-text\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><i class=\"icon icon-users\"></i></a>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"aw-comment-box\" style=\"display:none\">\n<div class=\"aw-comment-list\"></div>\n\n<a class=\"aw-load-more-content\">\n<span>更多</span>\n</a>\n\n<form action=\"/question/ajax/save_answer_discussion/answer_id-156313\" method=\"post\" onsubmit=\"return false\">\n<div class=\"aw-comment-box-main\">\n<textarea class=\"a